RAM TIHNGHIN RUAL LOH

Ram ka duh ber mai chu, ram tihnghin rual loh, chatuana awm hlen tur ngei chu a ni. Mi tin chhunga thlarau hian chu ram hlun tur chu a zawng ṭheuh ni hian ka ring ṭhin.
Lalram ropui eltiang a lo ding tawh ṭhin a. Babulon lalram, Lal Nebukadnezara hun laia lo ding tawhte chu namen lovin a ropui a, amah ngei pawh khawvel pumpui zar hliah khup khawpa thing buk lian tehkhin hial zu ni a. Rome lalramte hlei hlei tak kha aw, an khawpui ropuizia chu hahipin an sawi ṭhin a, ‘Rome khawpui hi ni khata sak a ni lo’ tih chu Rome khawpui ropuizia sawi fiah nan a tawk zo lo asin. Nimahsela chung ram ropuite chu a nghing a, a lo boral daih tawh a, an dinna mual pawh hriat fiah harsa khawpin tawnmang mai an chang tawh nia mawle.
Aigupta ram ropui laia lal ropui Pharoa lal lai hun te tak kha, kumkhua pawha chhe theia mawi a ni lo. Nimahsela thi thei mihring chu zuiin an rawih ral leh ṭhin. Chutiang zel chuan, Medo- Persia, Greek, Tura leh Sidon te chu an lalte ruh ro chawpin an tham ral tawh hlawm a ni si a.
Pathian hnam thlan bik, Israel chunga roreltu tura hriak thih Lal Saula te, Lal Davida te leh Lal Solomona te meuh pawh anmahni leh an lalṭhutthleng a hlun chuang lo va, thawnthu mai an chang zo tawh. Hun hian lui lian luang zel angin hring fate min len bo ṭhin a, ram tihnghin rual loh changtute chauh chu an nihlawh dawn a lo ni reng mai.
Kan tunlai khawvel inlumleh dan te tak hi. Khawvel buk zo hial khawpa thiltihtheihna kawltu Soviet Union te chu a keh darh thut a; mual letliama chêng ang maia thinlung lama lo inṭhen tawh, W.German leh E.German te chu zaikhatah luangin, Berlin Wall meuh tawh a chim nia ! Eng ang takin khawvel neitu nih chu German hnam thisen chuan chuh leh ang maw ? Khawvel puma nu leh pa chan chang theia inngai USA te hi a la chuai vek dawn tih hi rin a va har em ! Ram ni tla seng lova roreltu, Kumpinu sawrkar pawh hi hriat reng turin a ding dawn bik hauh lo. Ram tihnghin rual loh chu a va ngaihawm ṭhin em !
Thalai tawh phawtin an enghelh ber, nupaa insiamna te pawh hi zuk chhût chian ngat chuan inthihsan leh turin kan innei lek a lo ni tlat nia. Kan rila rah fanau rochan hlu ber, Pathian hnen ata kan dawnte pawh hi kan la ṭhen leh tur tho. “Kan inhmu leh tak ang em aw,” tih hi mihring tawpna huna lo inlar leh ṭhin chu a ni ngei tak a. Engmah lo maia chang leh tur inchuh ta reng rengin lal fing leh lal ropui ber berten an hun hlu an khawhral a. Mi tin hian thi leh thau pawlhin boral leh mai mai tur hi kan sual chamchi ṭhin zawng a nih hi. Ram kan duh ber tur chu ding hlen tur, ram tihnghin rual loh, Siamtu kutchhuak chauh chu a ni.
Khawpui mawi leh hmingthang, vawiin nia leia lalten an lu nghahnate hi chuai leh mai tura din an ni lo va. Nimahsela ṭiauchhum var hluk kan hmuh ṭhinte chu hriat loh hlana a lo bo leh duak ṭhin ang hian, chung khawpui hmingthang, en kham theih loh khawpa chhuanawm, mipui sang tam tak zik mur murna leh lirthei tinreng hawktui anga an luan dul dulna kawtthlêr chen hian mual an liam ni a la thleng ang. Lei hmasa leh van hmasa boral ni chuan Himalaya tlang paw vo mai chen hian sawn bovin a la awm dawn tlat si.
Tarho nun khawhar ṭhinzia tur te tak hi. An vanglai ni an ngai ṭhin. Naupan lai huna an ṭhian hluite chuan mual an liam zo tawh a, an ṭhat lai ni chu kawlah a her lliam daih tawh tih an hai bik lo. Khawtlang lunglen leh romei zam riai chuan an thinlungah khawharna chauh a rawn thlen tawh ṭhin. An tan siamtu kutchhuak ni êng mawi leh khawvel parte hi a zahawm thei hial awm asin maw. An dinhmun hriat thiampui khawpa finna nei an tlem si a. Ram tihnghin rual loh chu ngai ve vawng vawng te hian ka ring ṭhin.
Khawvel hnam ze tinreng nunphung leh khawsak dan danglam fê anga langte pawh hi he ram nghing ṭhin hmunah hi chuan kan chhungril khawharna hi chu a danglam teh chiam awm lo asin. Kan nun ruak inpho chhuak hi a lan dan a lo danglam mai zawk a. Inbum chawpna thinlung pu, Adama fateho hi tumah danglam bik reng an awm lo. Kan vun rawng danglamna leh kan chenna hmun leh nunphung danglamna piaha a chhunga cheng hring fate hi angkhat vek kan lo ni a. Hnam tinreng hi ram tihnghin rual loh chu mamawhtu kan lo ni.
Lal in chhunga dam chhung hun hmang zotute pawh hi bak berha ni tin ei chawp zawngtute nen hian angkhat reng tho an lo ni. Mi rethei te tete’n ke khi hrip hrepa hlimna an chhar chhuah ṭhin bâk hi lal in chhungah pawh a awm chuang lo. Mi retheite manganna leh neinungte nun ninna hi thil inchen chiah, thlan tur awm chuang lo a ni. Chuvangin mi dangte hmuhsit chin hi mahni anchhe inlawhna lek a lo a ni.
Mi thiamte hriatna nasa tak leh mi mawlte âtna pawh hi thil thuhmun a ni. Hriatna a punna apiangah buaina a pung ṭhin a, mihringte an mawlna apiangah tawrhna a tam thung. Chu buaina leh tawrhna chu a buklung rih lam chu angkhat reng a ni. Mi thiam leh mi mawlte-ah thil rit ber chu, chaponain thinlung a delh hian a ni. Chapona hi awm lo se, khawvel intlansiakna tam tak hi thil ṭul lo a ni tih kan hre chauh vang. Chapona chunga chuangin lungawina hmun a thlen theih hauh loh tih hi mihringten kan la zir chhuak chuang lo. Chapona kawl bun lo chu mi dang tan thil chimawm tak a tling. Mawhphurhna chauhvin chhelna min pe thei a, chhelna chauhvin finna tluantling min siam sak ṭhin a ni. Mawhphurhna hnartu chuan finna a chhar chhuak lo vang. Zirna chuan hriatna kawngah thui tak  min  hruai  thei  a,  finna  erawh  chu mawhphurhnain a nghawng chhuah, tawrhna avanga chhelna rah a ni si a.
Sakhaw hrang zuitute pawh hi thuhmun vek an ni ti ila thil awihawmah i ruat lo mai thei. An thil zawn chu lungawina te, hlimna te leh thlamuanna te hi a ni ṭheuh a. An inanna em em chu an thil zawn an hmu lo ṭheuh mai hi a ni. Sakhaw biakna inte chu danglam mah se, zawn hmu lo ṭheuh ṭheuh si chu, rinna kawnga an lungrual chho ta mai hi, an tih awm reng leh an au hla, “Sakhaw tin hian Pathian pakhat chu an pawh vek a, thuhmun vek an lo ni,” tia World Religious Congress leh Inter-Faith Festival a lo piang ta te hi dem tur a ni lo va, an tih awm reng ti an ni a. Hmuh inang ni lo va, hmuh loh inang na na na chuan, World Council of Churches an din pawh hi thil tih awm tak an ti a ni e.
Dr. Eugene Stockwell, the Chairman of WCC chuan, “Pathian Beram No Lal Isua Krista thisena sil fai loh sakhaw dang zuitu tam tak hian Pathian khawngaihna avangin chatuan nunna an chang ang,” (Many disciples of the non-Christian religions, none of whom will be washed in the blood of the Lamb, the Lord Jesus Christ, are to receive eternal life by God’s grace) zu han ti a. (World Conference on Mission & Evangelism in San Antonio, Texas, May 23,’89 - Christian News
12.6.’89). Pathian aiin chhandamna an siam zau thiam zawk a ni awm e. (John.14:6).
Ram tihnghin rual loh chu : Van boruak zau, tâwp chin awm lo, thengreng (universe) lam kan  hawi  chuan,  Sam  phuahtu  rilru  chu ṭawmpuiin, “I van i kut chhuak te, thla leh arsi i ruat-hote khi ka han ngaihtuah chang chuan...” tih loh theih loh hian Siamtu Pathian ropuizia a lo lang uar ṭhin. A ni tak a, chung lam arsi chhiar sen loh êng pe un khian Pathian ropuizia chu an hril chiang hle mai. Kan chenna lei (planet) hi lian hlein kan lo hre ṭhin a, nimahsela arsite lenzia chhût chuan kan chenna lei ve em hi chu sawi tham a ni mawlh lo. Arsi zinga a tê pawl, ni (sun) ngawt pawh khi kan chenna lei nena khaikhin ralah chuan lian hem hem tak a ni a, lei pum pui hi a siper lek zu ni a. Arsi tam tak chu a lêt maktaduai tam taka lian an ni hlawm. Chutiang taka lian arsite chu chhiar sen rual a ni lo ve.
Mihringte suangtuah phak rual loh khawpa chakin an tana kawng ruat sakah chuan an thlawk fur fur reng a. Second khat pawh han chawl det se universe khi a alh pup pup nghal mai dawn a lo ni. Fel taka rem a, an kawngte ruat saka, hun bite vawn saktu chu fak tlâk a va ni em ! A finna chu chhui chhuah rual a ni lo ve. Chung lam vana thil makte dintu chuan, mihringte hi min hre reng mai zu nia !
Thil mak chhui sen rual lohte dintu leh fel taka vawngtu chu mihringte anga lo piangin sual bawihah a insiam a, thi khawp hiala thu zawmin kan tan a inpe a, mahni inchhandam thei lovin min chhandam a, mihringte a hmangaihna chuan kraws-ah a khaikáng reng a. A thlarau thlah khawp hiala sual nunrawnna chuan a chunga ro a rel sak hnuah tlanna thisen chuan Pa lungawina chu ko kirin, amah chu kan felna atan thihna hneh zo vekin a tholeh a. Ram tihnghin rual loh chu a tlansate chanvo a lo ni ta. “Vawi khat chu lei chauh ni lovin, van pawh ka la tinghing ang,” ti lehtu chuan a hnenah min chentir ta si a.
Mi dik tak chuan a dikna ngei khenbeh chu mi sualte thih nan a thlang a. A thihna chu sual tana Pathian thilhlan a nih ang ngeiin, a hlantu Pathian thinlungah hnukchatin a hnenah phum vein kan lo awm ta ! Chu kraws hnehna azarah chuan nunna thar “KRISTA” chu kan nunna, sual thihsana kan pianna thar chu a ni.
Chu ram tihnghin rual loh chu mihring thinlung a ni mai lo va, mihring thinlung chhunga Pathian ram, Krista thawhlehna thiltihtheihna hmanga Thlarau Thianghlimin a din chu a ni a, Krista chenna a ni.
Mitthi khaw kulh kawngkharte chuan sipai chakna te, sakawlh thiltihtheihna te, mei khandaih te hmangin vawi duai lo chu ram chu tuk dawl an lo tum tawh a. Nimahsela a dotu a chhah zawh poh veleh, chu ram chu ram hlun tur a nih avangin a êng zual zawk ṭhin. Khawvel economic lo thlahniam mek leh nuclear war lo thleng tur lakah pawh Chungnungbera bihrukna hmun chu a nghing lo vang.
Tlang khawih theih, chhum dum te, thusawi thawm awmna ten a thlen phâk loh, fa tir vana hming chuang kohhranho chenna a ni a, chu ram chu engmahin a thleng phâk lo, Lalpa Pathian chenna ‘Zion’ a nih miau avangin.
 

Khawvel sakhaw tinreng leh lei lalṭhutthleng leh an ropuinate an zain an la boral ang a, a Fapa hmangaih taka ram erawh tunah leh chatuanin a ding reng ang. Kung zawng zawng phawia a awm ni chuan felna thing Lalpa phunte chu zuahin an awm ang. Chu ngei chu Krista hmangaihtute thinlung chhûng thurûk chu a ni. Chu ram tihnghin rual loh chu kan chan avangin khawngaihna i nei ang u (Heb.12:18-29; Sam 125:1).

“A lo kal dawn ropuina nen chhum chungah, A tlan sate min rawn hruai turin;
Lei hrehawm kan chhuahsanna ni chu a hnai
ta,
Halleluiah ! Ka lawm e, Lalpa.
Aw ka lawmna ber, ka Chhandamtu,
Ka thlamuanna leh ka hlimna hla ber i ni;
|hatnain a par ka thinlungah,
A chul lo ve ka Chhandamtu chu.”





